text: Hemicladus thomsonii is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Buquet in 1857. It is known from Brazil and Paraguay.BioLib.cz - Hemicladus thomsonii. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Calliini Category:Beetles described in 1857
title: Hemicladus thomsonii
